#: ../../source/how_to/compare_two_scenarios.rst:2
msgid "Compare two scenarios"
msgstr "对比两个情景"

#: ../../source/how_to/compare_two_scenarios.rst:4
msgid ""
"**Goal.** Quantify what changes between a baseline and a counterfactual "
"-- total cost, capacity mix, generation by carrier, LMPs."
msgstr "**目标。** 量化基线与反事实情景之间的差异——总成本、装机结构、按载体的发电量、LMP。"

#: ../../source/how_to/compare_two_scenarios.rst:8
msgid ""
"The result NetCDF makes side-by-side comparison easy: each file is just "
"an ``xarray.Dataset`` with the same variables, so subtraction and "
"`groupby` work directly."
msgstr ""
"结果 NetCDF 让并排比较变得简单:每个文件都是一个 ``xarray.Dataset``,变量名一致,因此可以直接做减法和 "
"`groupby`。"

